title: The Green Canteen - Mobile Van
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Western, Mediterranean, Fast food, Mexican, Catering, Take-out only
description: Vendor at Ambleside market on Wednesdays selling falafel pita and salad box, bean chilli and guacamole with bread or on nachos, a veggie burger of the day, and normally a special of the day like soup, dhal, or tacos. The core menu is vegan (as is the cake) with occasional dairy. Check its webpage for other event dates & catering info.
